I found the solution by myself. The problem is, that the data will be generated too fast before the modal is opened. So now i start the AJAX request after the modal is opened by using the "shown"-event instead of the "onclick"-event:

``` javascript
$('#modal').on('shown.bs.modal', function() {
    load_chartdata_by_ajax();
});
```
